own cells in order to repair itself.

39
00:05:09.228 --> 00:05:12.116
In biology. this is
called neurogenesis.

40
00:05:12.273 --> 00:05:14.072
Here. at GEN-SYS.

41
00:05:14.122 --> 00:05:17.745
we call it a cure to Alzheimer's.

42
