158
00:13:16.813 --> 00:13:18.341
My car keys. where'd you put 'em?

159
00:13:18.448 --> 00:13:23.179
Dad. ... you a. you don't drive anymore.

160
00:13:24.311 --> 00:13:26.419
I know that.

161
00:13:29.447 --> 00:13:30.694
Here ...

162
00:13:32.352 --> 00:13:35.529
