180
00:15:08.760 --> 00:15:13.098
He completed the Lucas Tower in
15 moves. a perfect score.

181
00:15:13.426 --> 00:15:17.793
I maintain my hypothesis that:
A. The green in his eyes indicate

182
00:15:17.929 --> 00:15:22.063
