267
00:22:11.909 --> 00:22:13.584
Yeah. I see that.

268
00:22:14.922 --> 00:22:17.864
We can at least give him some open space?

269
00:22:17.914 --> 00:22:20.132
- Yeah. That would prpbably be a good idea.

270
00:22:23.875 --> 00:22:26.610
